OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkraine rejects Putin's    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'trivial' Christmas truce  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Russian President Vladimir Putin has   
OL,6, ordered his defence minister to impose 
OL,7, a 36-hour ceasefire on the Ukrainian   
OL,8, frontline, beginning on Friday.        
OL,10,FThe ceasefire, scheduled to start at   
OL,11,F12:00 Moscow time (09:00 GMT), will    
OL,12,Fcoincide with the Russian Orthodox     
OL,13,FChristmas.                             
OL,15,FMr Putin asked Ukraine to reciprocate, 
OL,16,Fbut Kyiv quickly rejected the request. 
OL,18,FUkrainian presidential adviser Mykhailo
OL,19,FPodolyak called it a "propaganda       
OL,20,Fgesture".                              
